        {
            "title": "歐洲股市下跌 美伊停火延期前景堪憂",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"691\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/n_iovJ9fAx2hc.wQRj_Qog--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY5MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/100922de8fda0af6517264fddd1ab3db\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐洲股市下跌，因美國總統唐納德·川普表示延長停火「極不可能」，打擊了對伊朗戰爭結束的希望。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">斯托克歐洲600指數收跌。一籃子航空股下跌，布倫特原油位於每桶美元。汽車、銀行和工業等周期股也表現滯後。能源板塊表現優異。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者的樂觀情緒周一動搖，因川普表示，除非達成協議，否則他不會延長為期兩周的停火。美國周末在阿曼灣扣押了一艘伊朗船隻，伊朗則在重新封鎖霍爾木茲海峽後，向多艘船隻開火。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"691\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cRISqq32YefZ3j0Q3L6dtg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY5MQ--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b643d7c9e17fe74a2d639f4a25ed0ad4\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲股市尚未完全收復中東衝突爆發以來的全部失地。交易員正密切關注一系列企業財報，以期從中了解能源價格上漲對該地區企業的影響。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-61e0cb02-a277-382a-b491-0cbc0ad781d2-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們進行市場操作的假設是，當前的緊張局勢是暫時的，最終會達成協議，」Global Gate Asset Management首席投資策略師Patrik Lang表示，「我們認為，這只是短期波動，市場最終會擺脫這些干擾，重新關注更廣泛的前景。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">個股方面，Loomis AB下跌，此前高盛分析師將這家公司的評級下調至中性，稱市場已大多消化了良好的成長和利潤。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題European Stocks Drop on Worries Over Iran Ceasefire Extension</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
